The very first Wiki, created by WardCunningham. Its focus is on ExtremeProgramming and many other programming topics.

There is quite a lot of content concerning Forth, with many proponents claiming that Forth was using ExtremeProgramming techniques decades ago.

* http://c2.com/cgi/wiki
* http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?ForthLanguage -- the starting point for other Forth pages.  As here, you can click on the title to get a reverse link to all pages that mention Forth.
* http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?ForthWiki -- a list of other Forth Wiki
* http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?CategoryInManyProgrammingLanguages -- shows how Forth compares to other languages for many problems (EightQueens, etc.)
